OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLow cloud
OL,6,Falong the coast will spread inland
OL,7,Fthis evening driven by a moderate
OL,8,Fbreeze off the North Sea. Some fog
OL,9,Fpatches and isolated outbreaks of
OL,10,Flight rain or drizzle are possible.
OL,11,FStaying mild overnight.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FCloudy to start, gradually
OL,14,Fclearing for most. Sunshine
OL,15,Fdeveloping, but cloud may linger near
OL,16,Fcoasts and in the north. Cooler near
OL,17,Fcoasts especially in the breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
